textBody:
CJD can mean:
* Abbreviation for Chojoongdong, the three major newspapers in South Korea
* Christliches Jugenddorfwerk Deutschlands, a German Christian educational institution
* Creutzfeldt–Jakob disease, a rare disease of the brain caused by prions.
